================================================================================
Third-party content
================================================================================

This repository bundles or modifies third-party software that retains its
own license terms. The MIT license above applies to original work in this
repository (scripts, monitor, documentation, bat wrapper, etc.). The
following items are NOT covered by the MIT license:

- bin/d3d8.dll
    d3d8to9 v1.15.1 by crosire and contributors.
    Source: https://github.com/crosire/d3d8to9
    License: BSD-style (see upstream LICENSE in the d3d8to9 repository).
    Bundled here unmodified for convenience; verify the md5 in bin/SOURCE.txt
    if you do not wish to trust the bundled binary.

- patches/dynamic_entity_renamer.lua
    Patched derivative of the dynamic_entity_renamer addon by
    zach2good, TeoTwawki, and atom0s (distributed as part of the HorizonXI
    addon bundle).
    The upstream addon does not carry an explicit license header. This
    repository's modifications are minimal defensive patches (validation
    guards and a registry-cleanup hook) intended for personal-use defect
    mitigation under Wine. If you intend to redistribute the patched file,
    consult the upstream authors regarding license terms.
    See patches/dynamic_entity_renamer.lua.diff for a clear separation of
    the modifications from the original.
